    public class PackingStateFullCuts
extends PackingState
    A variant of packing state in which only full cuts can be made (cuts going through the whole width or height of the container).
    Author:
    Przemysław Klęsk (wi.zut.edu.pl), Marcin Korzeń (wi.zut.edu.pl)
